Interface Entity

All Known Subinterfaces:
EntityGroup, Model
public interface Entity

A representation of the model object 'Entity'.

Provisional API - subject to change

The following features are supported:

  • Child Entities
  • Traits
  • Id
  • Type
  • Include Groups
